User laurent.aphecetche@me.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -s mbsync-icloud-password -w"

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User laurent.aphecetche@gmail.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1
PassCmd "security find-generic-password -s mbsync-gmail-password -w"

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Maildir/gmail/
Inbox ~/Maildir/gmail/INBOX
Trash trash

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/Maildir/icloud/
Inbox ~/Maildir/icloud/INBOX
Trash trash

Channel icloud-inbox
Master :icloud-remote:
Slave :icloud-local:
Sync Pull New Flags 
Create Both 

Channel icloud-sent
Master :icloud-remote:
Slave :icloud-local:sent
Pattern "*Sent*"
Sync Pull New Flags 
Create Both 

Channel icloud-archive
Master :icloud-remote:Archive
Slave :icloud-local:archive
Sync Pull New Flags 
Create Both 

